{"tid":1426039,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局用4700億港幣同人民銀行換人民幣","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T14:32:03.000Z","uid":283494,"like":6,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2c88a4807457274c937f92c275336cb8276e3f","tid":1426039,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:23:40.000Z","msg":"新聞稿<br />\n中國人民銀行與香港金融管理局續簽貨幣互換協議<br />\n中國人民銀行與香港金融管理局今天公布，已續簽一份為期3年的貨幣互換協議。<br />\n協議規模為4,000億元人民幣，與先前的協議相同，相當於4,700億元港幣。<br />\n香港金融管理局<br />\n2017年11月27日"},{"pid":"14006f697a4fe9c462bb57cbc6685798ca329085","tid":1426039,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:24:22.000Z","msg":"問題如下,求銀行界人士解答。"},{"pid":"d6530918ee642faab118fdba7be47e4ab5d7e9e8","tid":1426039,"uid":112720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:25:52.000Z","msg":"金管局大水猛灌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d69bac39a457312a06fbd573a1cfd184841a9e","tid":1426039,"uid":118736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:28:20.000Z","msg":"2017<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4be265f333565541f195bebd647027e55ea09b9","tid":1426039,"uid":262557,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:28:34.000Z","msg":"港幣換廢紙"},{"pid":"8203540661881ba7b87d27ba53dfa4a5673d0d29","tid":1426039,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DoNOjLY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDoNOjLY.png&h=715dcec7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/082901_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.es